{
  "stem": "2916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During this seven weeks, we found out about decimation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Decimation meant that if you did something that was against the rules, you would be lined up in the morning and every 10th person would be shot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at one point, we were being punished by decimation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were told in the evening that in the morning we will be decimated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was the most horrible night of my life because I was petrified that my mother would be shot instead of me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the decimation meant that they would start counting, one, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, and the 10th one would be shot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then again, one, two, three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was so worried that I would be ninth, and my mother would be 10th, and I wouldn't bear it that she should be shot in front of me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother was petrified that I will be shot and she would make it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was an awful, awful night, and everybody cried all night long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- this would be a long story and I cannot take up the time-- but a miracle happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because during that night, there was an insurrection in a nearby factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Polish workers struck against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were brought in and interrogated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all night long, they were interrogated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans were too busy with them, and they forgot to decimate us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the morning came, and we stood on appel, and we were not decimated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went back to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a long story, but all I can tell you is that we lived through decimation.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
